    <item>
      <title>黄金零售商 Kitco 的网站因网络安全事件而中断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/gold-retailer-kitco-website-disrupted-in-cybersecuity-incident</link>
      <description><![CDATA[同时提炼黄金的北美贵金属零售商 Kitco Metals Inc. 表示，由于网络安全事件，其网站和在线商店无法使用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/gold-retailer-kitco-website-disrupted-in-cybersecuity-incident</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 20:35:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资公司 H.I.G.废弃未来独立科技基金的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/h-i-g-capital-scraps-plans-for-future-standalone-tech-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[H.I.G.据知情人士透露，Capital 放弃了未来筹集专门用于技术投资的资金池的计划，转而通过其更加多元化的工具进行押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/h-i-g-capital-scraps-plans-for-future-standalone-tech-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 20:30:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫表示正在追踪 Apple Watch 案件，禁令迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/white-house-says-it-s-tracking-apple-watch-case-with-ban-looming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于专利纠纷，拜登政府正在“追踪”美国即将禁止几乎所有 Apple Watch 销售，美国贸易代表有权否决该决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/white-house-says-it-s-tracking-apple-watch-case-with-ban-looming</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 20:27:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰金融科技 Bunq 在数据招聘热潮之后推出人工智能聊天工具</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/fintech-unicorn-bunq-offers-ai-chat-tool-after-data-hiring-spree</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲数字金融公司 Bunq 正在推出一款聊天机器人，允许用户查询自己的支出信息，该机器人是该公司在过去一年雇用了十几名数据专家后构建的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/fintech-unicorn-bunq-offers-ai-chat-tool-after-data-hiring-spree</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Masimo 首席执行官对解决 Apple Watch 裂痕持开放态度，但表示“Tango 需要两个人”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/masimo-masi-ceo-says-he-d-settle-apple-watch-rift-but-it-takes-two-to-tango</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Masimo Corp. 首席执行官 Joe Kiani 是一家医疗设备制造商的负责人，该制造商已将苹果公司的智能手表置于美国禁令的边缘，他表示他愿意与该公司达成和解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/masimo-masi-ceo-says-he-d-settle-apple-watch-rift-but-it-takes-two-to-tango</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 19:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉分析师对 2024 年电动汽车放缓的看法变得更加谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/tesla-analysts-turn-more-cautious-on-2024-as-ev-slowdown-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街对特斯拉公司的前景正在迅速恶化，至少有两名分析师在多日内对这家电动汽车制造商变得更加谨慎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/tesla-analysts-turn-more-cautious-on-2024-as-ev-slowdown-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 18:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙将收购 Telefonica 价值 22 亿美元的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/spain-orders-state-company-sepi-to-buy-up-to-10-of-telefonica</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙政府计划购买价值高达 22 亿美元的 Telefonica SA 股份，以期在沙特阿拉伯巩固自己在该公司的地位之际，保护该国最具战略意义的资产之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/spain-orders-state-company-sepi-to-buy-up-to-10-of-telefonica</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 17:03:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果告诉员工他们不能将手表买家推荐给百思买</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/apple-watch-sales-end-at-apple-aapl-not-walmart-wmt-best-buy-bby</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司即将停止在其美国实体店和在线商店销售其最受欢迎的智能手表，以遵守贸易监管裁决。虽然其他零售商可以继续销售这些设备，但苹果公司告诉员工，它不能让人们知道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/apple-watch-sales-end-at-apple-aapl-not-walmart-wmt-best-buy-bby</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 15:38:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
